Figure: http://i.imgur.com/0rYo01Z.png

Quadrilateral ABCD is similar to quadrilateral EFGH.
What is the value of x?

AD...............................
AD = AB
AD = 24

x................................
AD/DC = EH/HG
24 / 3(x + 2) = 18 / (2x + 7)
24 / (3x + 6) = 18 / (2x + 7)
24 * (2x + 7) = (3x + 6) * 18
48x + 168 = 54x + 108
168 = 6x + 108
60 = 6x
10 = x

Check............................
AD/DC = EH/GH
24 / 3(x + 2) = 18 / (2x + 7)
24 / 3(10 + 2) = 18 / (2(10) + 7)
24 / 3(12) = 18 / (20 + 7)
24/36 = 18/27
2/3 = 2/3
